      "title": "80 air tickets for workers leaving for Japan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Air tickets were handed over to 80 young workers through the IRO College of Education technical intern recruit Sri Lankan workers in Japan. The air tickets were handed over at the Gangaramaya temple in Colombo today. After receiving the tickets, the students were blessed by the Deputy Incumbent Gangaramaya Temple Dr. Kirinde Assaji Thera. Pix by Pradeep Dilrukshana"
      ],
